query:
INSERT INTO orderbook_snapshots (market_id, yes_best_ask, yes_best_bid, yes_asks, yes_bids, captured_at)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, NOW())
        ON CONFLICT (market_id) DO UPDATE SET
            yes_best_ask = $2,
            yes_best_bid = $3,
            yes_asks = $4,
            yes_bids = $5,
            captured_at = NOW()
